    <h1>Wix Privacy Policy Generator</h1>
    <p class="last-updated">Published July 18, 2026</p>

    <p>Wix does not include a built-in privacy policy generator. To create a privacy policy for your Wix website, you need a third-party generator that asks about your site's data practices and produces a compliant document you can add to your pages. A <a href="https://buildprivacypolicy.com/">free privacy policy generator for your Wix site</a> walks you through a step-by-step form covering data collection, third-party services, and applicable laws, then gives you a ready-to-publish policy in minutes with no signup required.</p>

    <p>Whether you run a Wix portfolio site, blog, online store, or service business, privacy laws and platform best practices expect you to have a privacy policy. This guide explains why your Wix site needs one, what it should cover, how to add it, and how to generate one quickly.</p>

    <nav class="toc">
      <p class="toc-title">Contents</p>
